<item>
            <title>[SOLR-446] TextResponseWriter should be able to work with SolrDocument and SolrDocumentList</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-446</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ResponseWriters should be able to write SolrDocuments the same way they write Documents.  This will be useful for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-303&quot; title=&quot;Distributed Search over HTTP&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-303&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-303&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; or other RequestHandlres that modify a SolrDocument and return the result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
